<body>
<div type="letter">
    <pb facs="3531590" n="1"/>
    <opener>
        <lb/>Viro Summo, ac Mathematico Incomparabili Dan. Bernoullio
        <lb/>Greg. Fontana S. D.
    </opener>
    <p>
        <lb/>Patere, Bernoulli doctissime, ut ignotus homo, sed Tui admirator maximus
        <lb/>Te tantisper delineat, ac de re sane elegantissima interpellet.
    </p>
    <p>
        <lb/>In eximio tuo Hydrodynamic<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Opere Sect. X apodictiri, ni fallor, ostendis,
        <lb/>pressionem aeris supra datam terrestris superficiei plagam, in statu permanen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ti <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quilibrii, haudquaquam <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quipollere ponderi column<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> aere<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> absoluto,
        <lb/>sed po tius <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>stimandum esse ex pondere, quod invenitur capiendo termi<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>num quartum proportionalem ad <choice><orig><g ref="#etlig">&amp;</g></orig><reg>et</reg></choice>c. Id ipsum iterato inculcas in egregia
        <lb/>Dissertatione de Maris Aestu. Nobilis Geometra Alembertus in Opusculo
        <lb/>De Generali Ventorum Causa scrupulum injecit hominibus de Theorema<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tis illius tui veritate; atque alii postea Alemberto animosiores Theorema
        <lb/>ipsum aperte impugnarunt. Verum nihil me hactenus movit, ut de illius
        <lb/>veritate dubitarem. Miratus equidem sum, Te nihil de illo Theoremate
        <lb/>loqui in binis Opusculis ad Physicam Generalem spetantibus tomo I, et
        <lb/>II Actorum Helveticorum insertis ubi magna erat loquendi opportunitas,
        <lb/>ac fere necessitas; et suspicari quasi coepi, Te ipsum in aliam abiisse senten<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tiam. Quod me aliquantulum sollicitum habet (dicam enim quod res est)
        <lb/>huc refertur; quod si nimirum barometri tubus ex altera parte inflex<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>us produceretur usque ad supremam athmosp<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>r<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> altitudinem mercurius
        <lb/>in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>quilibrio persisteret, et in eadem, uti prius, altitudine suspenderetur,
        <lb/>cum tamen in hoc eventu prematur absoluto aereae columnae pondere.
        <lb/>Hac itaque de re tuam valde cupio mentem cognoscere, hujusque mei
        <lb/>desiderii h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c est ratio: Sub pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>lo habeo Opusculum propediem in lucem
        <lb/>exiturum De Barometricis Altitudinibus, nec non Insignibus quibusdam Pa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc>
        <pb facs="3531591" n="2"/>
        <lb break="no"/>radoxis huc referendis. Rem totam evolve per sublimiorem Analysim, dataque
        <lb/>occasione Theorematis illius tui mentionem injicio, illudque ut vertissimum
        <lb/>propono, atque in tuas laudes libere excurro. Vides igitur quan topere opus
        <lb/>habeam tuam hac de re cognoscere sententiam, nec non sententi<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> rationes,
        <lb/>si priorem mutaveris. Id mihi pergratum erit, tibique ob id devinctis<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>simus ero.
    </p>
    <p>
        <lb/>Paratas habeo Dissertationes aliquot meas Philologicas, atque etiam Mathe<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>maticas, prima occasione ad Te transmittendas una cum Operibus Fratris
        <lb/>mei Abb. Felicis Fontan<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Magni Etruri<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Ducis Mathematici, et Rei
        <lb/>Monetari<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> apud Florentinos Pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>fecti.
    </p>
    <p>
        <lb/>Lego nunc volumen secundum Calculi Integralis (tertium enim nondum
        <lb/>vidi) magni Euleri conterranei tui. 0 per quot novas regiones ducit
        <lb/>me summus hic Analysta, magni Johannis Parentis tui vere dignus disci<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>pulus. Scire cuperem, utrum Lunaris Theoria Geometr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> hujus adhuc lu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cem aspexerit, et num credendum sit, perductam ab eo fuisse ad eum per<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fectionis apicem, ut paucis secundis ab observationibus deficiat, uti in
        <lb/>nescio quibus Nunciis Litterariis memini me legisse; quemadmodum legi
        <lb/>nunc magno hercle dolore, combustam Petropoli fuisse Euleri domum,
        <lb/>ipsumque vix fuga ex incendio evasisse. Perierint igitur pretiosissima illius
        <lb/>Manuscripta? Audiam a Te aliquid certi de hac calamitate, nisi tibi erit mo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>lestum. Rogo demum Te, Vir summe idemque humanissime, ne dedigneris
        <lb/>narrare mihi num ex Filiis tuis aliquis sit, qui Mathesim pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>clare tra<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>ctet, quod sane jam a s<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>culo Famili<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> vestr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> est jus quoddam h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>reditarium
        <lb/>et utrum Johannes ille Bernoullius, qui nunc Berlini Astronomiam colit
        <lb/>sit notus ac doctissimus magni Johannis filius, tuusque Frater, an alius.
        <pb facs="3531592" n="3"/>
        <lb/>Ignosce, Vir humanissime, importunitati me<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>. Tanta est mea erga Te
        <lb/>et Familiam tuam ad miratio, ut omnia, qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ad vos spectant, mihi carissima
        <lb/>sint. Vale, Vir Incomparabilis, mequi tui amantissimum ama.
    </p>
    <closer>
        <dateline>
            <lb/>Dat. Ticini Kal. <date when="1771-09">Sept. ann. 1771</date>
        </dateline>
    </closer>
    <closer>
        <lb/>Voici mon adresse; s'il vous plaira, Monsieur m'honorer
        <lb/>de votre réponse qui pourra bien étre en latin, ou en fran<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>cois, que j'entends fort bien: A Monsieur
        <lb/>Monsieur le trés Reverend Pere Grég. Fontana
        <lb/>Professeur Public de Mathematique dans la
        <lb/>Royale Université de
        <lb/>Pavie
    </closer> 
    <pb facs="3531593" n="4"/>
    <closer>
        <address>
            <addrLine>À Monsieur</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Monsieur Daniel Bernoulli</addrLine>
            <addrLine>Trés-celebre Mathematicien</addrLine>
            <addrLine>dans la Suisse Bâle</addrLine>
        </address>
    </closer> 
</div>
